com.wingman.client.classloader

Class TransformingClassLoader

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.ClassLoader
      • java.security.SecureClassLoader
        • java.net.URLClassLoader
          • com.wingman.client.classloader.TransformingClassLoader
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Closeable, java.lang.AutoCloseable

    public class TransformingClassLoader
extends java.net.URLClassLoader
    TransformingClassLoader enables support for injection by Transformers.
    It only transforms classes residing in the com.wingman package and its subpackages plus classes owned by the RuneScape gamepack.
